'''Matt Bouchard''', an [[Industrial Light & Magic|ILM]] employee, worked as a digital effects artist for [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']]. Other notable works include being a visual effects technical assistant for [[Wikipedia:Flubber|''Flubber'']], and digital artist for [[Wikipedia:Shark Tale|''Shark Tale'']], [[Wikipedia:War of the Worlds (2005 film)|''War of the Worlds'']], and [[Wikipedia:Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest|''Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest'']].

